		<p>Nadine is the owner of the candy-colored Instagram <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sparklecious/"><b>sparklecious</b></a> . Her eye for design has helped her amass a dedicated online following. Just one look at her rainbow filled feed and you'll be hooked!</p><br>
