	<p><b><b>If you had to get rid of all of your dolls except one, which one would you save and why? <b></b></b></b></p>
	<p>Argh! Too hard! Every time I pick a girl up I’m convinced she’s the ONE. Then I pick up another and she’s the one…and so on.</p><br>
	<br>
	<br></b>
